data.description: Stunning Bungalow in the Heart of East Atlanta! Located STEPS to the Village, offering Locally-Owned Shops, Restaurants, Farmers Market, and more. Step inside to be greeted by Hardwood Floors that flow between the Light-Filled Family Room and the Dining Room with a Fireplace and Built-In Shelving. A Bright, White Kitchen offers Ample Shelving, Butcher Block Countertops, and Rear Patio Access. Two Spacious Bedrooms share a well-appointed Hall Bathroom with a Tiled Bathtub. Outside, a Rear Patio overlooks a Large, Fully Fenced Backyard - perfect for Gardening, Pets, or Play! STEPS to Burgess-Peterson Elementary School, Bookish Atlanta, Joe's Coffeehouse, The Midway Pub, and Minutes to I-20 offering an Easy Commute!
